                  <rs id="t18770507-453-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18770507-453-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18770507-453-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>, Feloniously forging and uttering an order for the payment of 10<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., with intent to defraud,</rs> to which Stewart <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18770507-453-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18770507-453-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
